OL,3,CSecondary school bans mobile phones
OL,4,Cand smartwatches
OL,6,FA secondary school has announced it
OL,7,Fwill be "mobile phone free" saying
OL,8,Fthey are a distraction to learning.
OL,10,FArk Alexandra Academy in Hastings,
OL,11,FSussex is asking for phones and
OL,12,Fsmartwatches to be left at home with
OL,13,Fparents or carers.
OL,15,FThe new school policy will start from
OL,16,Fthis academic year (September 2024)
OL,17,Fand the school says bag searches will
OL,18,Fbe carried out, in line with DfE
OL,19,Fpolicy.
