OL,6,FIt also said it looked at alternative
OL,7,Foptions, for pupils to store devices
OL,8,Fon site, but said the challenge of
OL,9,Fsecuring 2,000 phones on a daily basis
OL,10,Fwas not "practicable."
OL,12,FIn a video message uploaded on the
OL,13,Fschool's YouTube channel, Vice
OL,14,FPrincipal Sarah Butters said: "In
OL,15,Fresponse to updated guidance from the
OL,16,FDepartment of Education, and simply
OL,17,Fbecause it is the right thing to do,
OL,18,FArk Alexandra will become mobile free
OL,19,Ffrom September 2024.
