OL,3,CSecondary school bans mobile phones
OL,4,Cand smartwatches
OL,6,F"That means that students must leave
OL,7,Ftheir phones at home with their parent
OL,8,For carer. Phones will not be permitted
OL,9,Fin school at all.
OL,11,F"This rule also applies to other
OL,12,Finternet enabled devices such as smart
OL,13,Fwatches. The school will not look
OL,14,Fafter devices during the school day as
OL,15,Fwe do not have the resource and cannot
OL,16,Ftake on the liability for the
OL,17,Fcollection and distribution of what
OL,18,Fwould be 1,800 phones.
