OL,6,F"Students who carry or conceal devices
OL,7,Fon their person or in their bag will
OL,8,Fbe in breach of school policy. Bag
OL,9,Fsearches will take place in line with
OL,10,FDfE guidance and the school's behavior
OL,11,Fpolicy."
OL,13,FThe school says it is engaging with
OL,14,Ffamilies who are finding these
OL,15,Fadjustments more challenging and
OL,16,Fsupporting individuals where
OL,17,Fadjustments are necessary.
