OL,6,FA statement from Rhys Spiers,
OL,7,FExecutive Principal, said: "Mobile
OL,8,Fphones are a distraction to learning
OL,9,Fand are so often at the core of mental
OL,10,Fhealth issues impacting children.
OL,12,F"We want our school to be an
OL,13,Fenvironment where healthy
OL,14,Frelationships, respect and courtesy
OL,15,Ffor one another are hallmarks of our
OL,16,Fcommunity.
