OL,6,F"We have proactively communicated with
OL,7,Fparents and students about the changes
OL,8,Fto our mobile phone policy, which has
OL,9,Falready led to a significant uplift in
OL,10,Fstandards across the academy.
OL,12,F"We're actively engaging with families
OL,13,Fwho are finding these adjustments more
OL,14,Fchallenging and supporting individuals
OL,15,Fwhere adjustments are necessary."
